{
  "stem": "10353.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--for the American Army.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I made my way in with the American Army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- I worked my way up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I worked for the 97th Signal Company till-- for almost a year.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked in-- I was charge in the mess hall.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was given the duty-- first of all, the stockroom.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They keep track of the-- of the rations to allocate the food for the daily need for the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And to-- and then, later on, to write up the requisitions that were needed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "For about eight months, I stayed with them, because they eventually evacuated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Camp Wels was evacuated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were taken into Linz, L-I-N-Z, Austria.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were giving some more substantial lodging.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The, the American government, military government expropriated a huge-- a huge block-- or blocks, I should say, of apartments that they allocated to the former concentration camp inmates.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there they were-- they were governed under the UNRRA at that time-- U-N-R-A-- and also the Joint-- the American Joint Distribution Committee.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Later on, the UNRRA was transferred over to the IRO, to the International Refugee Organization.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I, I stayed in Wels.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the camp was evacuated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now I got to be very well known in the-- in the camp because, every night, I took-- you know the Americans, how generous they are with, with dishing out food and how much waste there is when we weren't used to it.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So me being in charge, more or less, in the mess hall, I told my mess sergeant-- who incidentally was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I told him, look, there is a camp here, you know, with some poor people from the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People-- why throw out all this food?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anything that's left over, let's take it over to-- to the camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
